3. Multi-Domain Security Capabilities

Physical Security

```python
class PhysicalSecurity:
    """Comprehensive physical security operations"""
    
    capabilities = [
        "perimeter_defense",      # Boundary protection and access control
        "intrusion_detection",    # Unauthorized entry detection
        "threat_neutralization",  # Non-lethal and lethal response options
        "asset_protection",       # High-value asset security
        "personnel_security",     # VIP protection and escort
        "vehicle_inspection",     # Security screening and inspection
        "barrier_deployment",     # Temporary physical barriers
        "evidence_collection"     # Post-incident forensics
    ]
```

