ðŸ“Š Security Metrics & KPIs

Metric Description Target Measurement
Threat Detection Rate Percentage of threats detected â‰¥99.9% ROC curve analysis
False Positive Rate Incorrect threat identifications â‰¤0.1% Statistical analysis
Response Time Time from detection to response â‰¤1 second Time tracking
System Uptime Security system availability â‰¥99.99% System monitoring
Compliance Rate Adherence to security standards 100% Audit results
Intrusion Prevention Successful intrusion blocks â‰¥99% Penetration testing
Data Protection Data confidentiality/integrity 100% Security audits
Recovery Time Time to recover from breach â‰¤1 hour Disaster recovery tests

ðŸ›¡ï¸ Defense-in-Depth Implementation

```python
class DefenseInDepth:
    """Implement defense-in-depth security strategy"""
    
    async def deploy_defense_layers(self):
        """Deploy multiple layers of defense"""
        
        layers = {
            "perimeter_defense": await self.deploy_perimeter_defense(
                physical_barriers=True,
                electronic_surveillance=True,
                access_controls=True,
                intrusion_detection=True
            ),
            "network_defense": await self.deploy_network_defense(
                segmentation=True,
                firewalls=True,
                intrusion_prevention=True,
                network_monitoring=True
            ),
            "host_defense": await self.deploy_host_defense(
                endpoint_protection=True,
                application_whitelisting=True,
                patch_management=True,
                behavioral_analysis=True
            ),
            "data_defense": await self.deploy_data_defense(
                encryption=True,
                access_controls=True,
                data_loss_prevention=True,
                backup_recovery=True
            ),
            "personnel_defense": await self.deploy_personnel_defense(
                training=True,
                background_checks=True,
                least_privilege=True,
                monitoring=True
            ),
            "physical_defense": await self.deploy_physical_defense(
                secure_facilities=True,
                environmental_controls=True,
                power_protection=True,
                redundant_systems=True
            )
        }
        
        # Cross-layer correlation and response
        correlation = await self.correlate_across_layers(layers)
        response_coordination = await self.coordinate_response(correlation)
        
        return {"layers": layers, "correlation": correlation, "coordination": response_coordination}
```

